Package: bayesRates
Version: 1.0
Title: Two-Sample Tests and Sample Size Determination from a Bayesian Perspective
Description: bayesRates allows you to calculate the sample size required for
    two-sample tests of binomial proportions and Poisson rates with given 
    operating characteristics.
URL: https://github.com/dkahle/bayesRates
BugReports: https://github.com/dkahle/bayesRates/issues
Authors@R: c(person("David", "Kahle", email = "david.kahle@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
  person("Ryan", "Sides", email = "ryan_sides@lilly.com", role = "aut"),
  person("James", "Stamey", email = "james_stamey@baylor.edu", role = "aut"))
